cat << EOF
Lightspark is a modern, free, open-source flash player
implementation. Lightspark features:

* JIT compilation of Actionscript to native x86 bytecode using LLVM *
Hardware accelerated rendering using OpenGL Shaders (GLSL) * Very good and
robust support for current-generation Actionscript 3 * A new, clean, codebase
exploiting multithreading and optimized for modern hardware. Designed from
scratch after the official Flash documentation was released.
